headline: Apply Now: Accessibility Improvement Grant Portal Opens for L.A. Interim Housing Providers
summary: Brilliant Corners, in collaboration with the Los Angeles County Department of Health Services Housing for Health Division, L.A. Care Health Plan, and Health Net, announced the launch of a new website for interim housing providers in Los Angeles County to apply for accessibility-related construction grants. The official website for the Interim Housing Accessibility Improvement Fund opens on August 27, 2025, at 12:00 p.m. PST, with applications accepted on a rolling, first-come, first-served basis
